== INITIAL DEPLOYMENT

Prerequisits:
* ruby (ree-1.8.7-2011.03, ruby-1.9.2 p 180)
* postgresql (tested on  9.*)
* libxml-dev
* libmagick++
* libpq-dev

Environment setup:

  $ gem install bundler
  $ bundle install
  $ cp config/database.yml.example config/database.yml

Edit your database.yml. Fill it with dbname and user credentials.

Create development database.

  $ rake db:create
  $ rake db:migrate

== TESTING

After initial deployment everything is ready to run cucumber features.

  $ rake cucumber

